        "description": "The hadoop dependencies seem a bit messed up.  We have a hadoop.version set in the main pom.xml to 2.6.0 but it does not really appear to be used.  storm-core uses hadoop-auth set to 2.4.0, storm-hdfs hard codes it to 2.2.0, storm-hbase does the same.  We should have all of the versions be consistent and come from the main pom.xml.  Also what are we using hadoop-auth for in storm-core.\n\nAlso it looks like we should remove the hadoop-auth dependency.  When AutoHDFS and AutoHBase moved out of storm-core it looks like it was left there by mistake. ",
